results.description: Cassondra Castle is old, her time is coming to an end, but there are still plenty who need punishment. Her son, Franklin, has never known her terrible secret... where she spent her evenings. But now, someone has to pick up the torch, continue the legacy. Franklin Castle's life is about to change. Forever.
